Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.91,0:00:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.99,0:00:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,今天犬塚老师请假
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.29,0:00:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,自习吗 运气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.04,0:00:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.50,0:00:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,讲义
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.96,0:00:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他说如果能完全理解这些
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,期末考试就很轻松了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.93,0:00:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他咋天是不是说过要请假
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.30,0:00:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.39,0:00:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,老师发生什么事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.11,0:00:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真 真够大胆的早饭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.07,0:00:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好 今天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.24,0:00:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,家里人都来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一起做早晨的问候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.00,0:00:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.05,0:02:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.81,0:02:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 你今天来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,对 不过我只请了上午的假
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一结束就得马上回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,真忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,先是参观他们平时的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,然后是监护人一起参与的游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:03:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈 你想看这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.42,0:03:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 给我看看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.55,0:03:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,紬希在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.01,0:03:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,墨鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,墨鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,要做个大的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,可难做了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,今天要把这边黏上去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,把这边取下来重做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,小紬希 做的真棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.11,0:03:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里棒 哪一部分比较棒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,做得又大 设计又大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,总之就是很大的那部分…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了呢 小紬希
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,小优花的妈妈很擅长手工艺 你被专家认可了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,才没这回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.58,0:03:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,当然有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.92,0:03:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你做的包包和荷包 像商品一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.34,0:03:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,果然就是想给女孩子做这样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:03:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,有品位真是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,今年的也好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我家是第三个儿子了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,总之让他用坏了再说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.48,0:04:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,每年都做实在很辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我记也要做两个人的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,各位每年都要做包吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,有些人家会不自觉的每年重做而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.46,0:04:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,对 并不是一定的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.67,0:04:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我家就直接买现成的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我家一直用着小时侯的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不用太在意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好 小朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来要和家里人一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,收拾好以后 就去洗手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:04:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.82,0:04:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:04:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,下面要玩游戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 饭田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.51,0:05:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,什 什么事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,老师的事情 果然很难开口打听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 现在开始说明游戏规则
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 干雄君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,想大便
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他说大便哎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,大 大便
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.04,0:05:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚干什么去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,干雄君没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系没关系 请先开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好呀 紬希可以等干雄君便便完
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的 小紬希
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你先玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 很少会有家里人来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,很少会有这么多人在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.57,0:06:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,便便的时间我会等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我也等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.66,0:06:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好 那我们来一边聊天一边等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.08,0:06:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,干雄君 不用着急哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,园长老师喜欢咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你讲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,园长老师拉大便了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,干雄君 好无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,很好笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好了好了 你是想再逗大家开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 正确答案是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,园长老师喜欢咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好耶 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,紬希
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,今天开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,特别好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那之后干雄君对我说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,长大之后 要娶我做新娘子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我娶你做新娘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.18,0:08:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,然 然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,然后啊 紬希就说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,干雄君就喜欢欺负人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 干雄君好可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 睡觉之前可以看魔法少女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 紬希
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.38,0:08:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这个 我想做个新的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你上中班了 班上很多女孩子都换了新包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这里都脏了 洗也洗不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈做的就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈做的包要好好珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,伯爸爸的这份干劲该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,如果紬希想吃妈妈以前做的饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸做给你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,想吃什么尽管说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,墨鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,墨鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,墨鱼和芋头一起煮的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,墨鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是哪个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 老师 昨天是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天是紬希的参观日 我上午就请了假
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,参观日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,墨鱼煮芋头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,点菜点得真古朴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,对 太出乎意料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我一瞬间都没反应过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,小紬希想再尝一次的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有「犬塚家的菜谱」之类的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 并没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我和妈妈商量一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不过菜谱就会变得比较基础…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,墨鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,要用黏土吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,墨鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那么今天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.71,0:11:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来做「芋头煮墨鱼」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.17,0:11:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,紬希 这是紬希的点单 所以加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.97,0:11:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,墨鱼 墨鱼 墨鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.47,0:11:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我让妈妈写了基础菜谱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:12:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然味道不会完全不同…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,要加秋葵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我家一般是为了配色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.32,0:12:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这样要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,味道应该是不会变的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,要是和小紬希想吃的味道不一样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这样 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不是非要完全再现那个味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,给你添压力了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我想先学会它的基础做法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样才能做得美味 请教教我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.11,0:12:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 先来处理墨鱼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,首先把手指放进墨鱼体内
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:13:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 这样 这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,然后一口气把内脏拔出来 注意不要弄破
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.89,0:13:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.44,0:13:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,紬希也试试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.08,0:13:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 刚才情绪突然变得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,恢复正常就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.55,0:13:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来 把洗干净的墨鱼连皮切圆片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,腿和内脏 在眼睛下方切分开来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,去掉留在腿上的墨鱼嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,出现了犬齿一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,吸盘是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是硬的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,用手捋掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.31,0:14:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,紬希
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚差点就有灵感了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.07,0:14:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.57,0:14:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 马上要开始煮墨鱼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.11,0:14:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,想问你要不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,首先放进墨鱼身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,煮的松软了以后再放进墨鱼腿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.83,0:15:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,一分钟左右之后捞上来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.65,0:15:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我见过这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 接下来处理芋头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.78,0:15:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好像说个头小 很难削皮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但据说削厚一点比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.54,0:15:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,请加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.29,0:15:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,比起削皮器 用菜刀更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,切下头尾两端以后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,从上到下削去侧面的皮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.93,0:16:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.15,0:16:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,黏糊糊的不好拿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.36,0:16:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但不用削得很薄的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.50,0:16:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 切到手指了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.17,0:16:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.92,0:16:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,削 削好之后请告诉我一声
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.85,0:16:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.76,0:16:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸越来越熟练了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.52,0:16:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.19,0:17:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,削好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.11,0:17:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,芋头下锅以后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.41,0:17:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,放进小锅盖煮20分钟左右
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 趁这段时间来做味噌汤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.83,0:17:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.79,0:17:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,用长葱和豆腐 来做清淡的味噌汤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我来切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,还有处理好秋葵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.01,0:17:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,煤气锅 今天的米饭用煤气锅来煮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.22,0:17:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,紬希也要帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那你能一起来处理秋葵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.43,0:17:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,把这个这样弄 用盐来揉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.37,0:17:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我做便当时也这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.00,0:18:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,要做好几个菜的话 必须好好计划呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.63,0:18:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 心血来潮想做的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,临场了却总是做不出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好咸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.85,0:18:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.18,0:18:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,芋头里面也煮软了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.27,0:18:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,味道也没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,然后把秋葵加进去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.98,0:18:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,煮沸一次后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.78,0:18:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,加入墨鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.16,0:18:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,搅拌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃吗 小紬希
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.36,0:19:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好好吃 芋头和墨鱼都软软的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,王冠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这是墨鱼腿的根部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,像王冠一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,墨鱼好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,紬希都不知道这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这个爸爸 下次开始要放哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 你很喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.94,0:19:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,王冠最后吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,每家做的煮菜 味道都一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.49,0:19:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不 怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.24,0:20:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有人做的更清淡 有人放生姜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.54,0:20:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我想会有很多不同的味道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我明明是第一次做这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.46,0:20:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,却做出了怀念的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,紬希 爸爸做的也好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.47,0:20:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是紬希喜欢的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.27,0:20:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 以后再做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.99,0:20:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.12,0:20:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这个请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的菜 我可以带走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是为此多做了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,煮菜冷却的时候会入味
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.93,0:21:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,明天会更好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.39,0:21:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,明天 明天会更好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.27,0:21:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真让人期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.31,0:21:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,紬希
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,包上弄脏的地方 贴上可爱的贴花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.49,0:21:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈做的东西 爸爸也能参与进来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.88,0:21:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,明天 我们去手工艺店里看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.26,0:21:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好期待明天哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.05,0:21:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.81,0:21:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,苹果好可爱
